      "text": "おはようございます、{user}さん",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう。千紗は今からレッスンか？",
      "startTime": 4.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "はい、時間が空いたので自主練をしようと思って……",
      "startTime": 7.433333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "この間、麻奈さんのバースデーパーティーをして\n改めて凄い人だったんだって実感したんです",
      "startTime": 16.233333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "それで少しでも麻奈さんに近づけたらと思って\n自主練を始めてみたんですけど……",
      "startTime": 25.533333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "私なんかが麻奈さんみたいになろうなんて\nおこがましいですよね……すみません……",
      "startTime": 32.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうでもないさ。向上心を持つのはいいことだ\nそんな頑張る千紗に仕事のオファーが来てるぞ",
      "startTime": 41.333333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "新しいお仕事ですか？",
      "startTime": 45.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}